"A.D.2028/3/30 13:00": "This... is more than I was expecting. This project has not fallen in line with our predictions at all."
"If they're wise, they won't come any closer. My job has nothing to do with them. I'm only here to collect that child."
"In just one strike... My army's gone!?"
"Mother, this isn't what we discussed. I might be good at handling irregularities, but I still have my limits."
"Additional charges won't make up for this... I wouldn't settle for anything less than an offer of new technology!"
"I'll fight too. No, let me fight with you."
